      'measured in pascals, never in newtons alone.',
    targetedMisconceptions: [`${SSTR}:MC-STRESS-IS-FORCE`],
    source: `${SSTR_SRC} — Component 1 MC-STRESS-IS-FORCE conflict_evidence [P28] (thick vs. thin bar, same force)`,
