    source: `${DMAT_SRC} — MC-DM-MIXED-IS-SUPERPOSITION (mixed state is a classical ensemble, not a coherent superposition) + MC-DM-PARTIAL-TRACE-LOSES-INFO (partial trace preserves local quantum information within A)`,
